## Spatial Audio
Unity: AudioSource → Spatial Blend = 1 (3D).
Plugin: Resonance Audio veya Steam Audio (binaural HRTF).
```csharp
AudioSource src = GetComponent<AudioSource>();
src.spatialBlend = 1.0f;
src.rolloffMode = AudioRolloffMode.Logarithmic;
src.maxDistance = 20f;
// Steam Audio Spatializer: Inspector'dan seç
```

